title: 18th Anniversary | Post-Event Recap
body_text:
The secret is out..
Dan Spengeman
is ECD's 21st HOF Inductee!
Plus.. Lenny was there. Pierce was there. Juan, Pam, & their son Fitzwilliam were there.
Need I say more about ECD's largest event in ten years? Here's a quick recap with bonus photos! 🙂
